Description: A toolkit for mapping and measuring natural capital and ecosystem services (in 
    the UK) using widely available national datasets. A re-write and update of the 
    defunct [Ecoserv-GIS tool](https://www.nature.scot/doc/naturescot-research-report-954-ecoserv-gis-v33-toolkit-mapping-ecosystem-services-gb-scale).
